Step 1 : Start

Step 2 : Read the number n for the Addition of all even numbers

Step 3 : Initialize the variable i with 0 and sum with 0

Step 4 : Check whether i is equal to n

Step 5 : If the condition returns true then directly print the value of sum

Step 6 : If the condition returns false then check whether the i is even number or not

Step 7 : If the i is even then add sum and i and assign it to the sum 

Step 8 : Then Increment the value of i with 1

Step 9 : If the i is not even then directly increment the value i with 1

Step 10 : Repeat steps 4 to 9

Step 11 : Stop

